esktop  and double click on the  My Password Information  icon  cadets will need to use a domain computer located in a lab to see this icon    If your password is to expire on or before 30 April  Please change your password now using the current system  Self Service Password  Log off the network and then log back on  Register in the new system www vmi edu SSPRegistration  If your password is going to expire after 30 April you do not need to change your password at this time  Please proceed to registering in the new SSP application www vmi edu SSPRegistration  The registration process consists of logging in with your network username and password  and then selecting several security questions   Registering is the only active feature available at this time  Full functionality will be available 30 April  When you register in the new system  you will automatically be unregistered in the current Self Service Password application  For detailed registration instructions please see the article  Registering in Self Service Password  by clicking the  Self Service Password  link on www vmi edu it If you have any questions  please call the Help Desk at 7643 or email Help vmi edu  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 